{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Fix no audio: add macOS audio entitlement + set volume\n\n- Add com.apple.security.device.audio-input to both entitlements\n- Explicitly set volume to 100 on play()\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
